org.apache.ignite.ml.math.primitives.matrix.impl

Class DenseMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.math.primitives.matrix.AbstractMatrix
      • org.apache.ignite.ml.math.primitives.matrix.impl.DenseMatrix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, Destroyable, MetaAttributes, Matrix, OrderedMatrix, StorageOpsMetrics

    public class DenseMatrix
extends AbstractMatrix
implements OrderedMatrix
    Basic implementation for matrix. This is a trivial implementation for matrix assuming dense logic, local on-heap JVM storage based on double[][] array. It is only suitable for data sets where local, non-distributed execution is satisfactory and on-heap JVM storage is enough to keep the entire data set.
